.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: apricot, lilac, grey, black, turquise
There are 5 different nationalities: brazilian, french, mexican, nigerian, russian
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-almond-milk, juice, almond-milk, 7up, fanta
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: apricotmaster, tiparillo, montecristo, davidoff, havana
5 different pets are kept: rabbit, chinchilla, rat, goat, frog
1. the brazilian is the person who likes grey
2. the swedish is the owner of the rat
3. the french is the person drinking 7up
4. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes black
5. the person who likes lilac is the person drinking juice
6. the montecristo-smoker is the owner of the chinchilla
7. the person who likes turquise is the tiparillo-smoker
8. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle
9. the nigerian is on the far left
10. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit
11. the owner of the frogs is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker
12. the apricotmaster-smoker is the person drinking soy-almond-milk
13. the mexican is the davidoff-smoker
14. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot
15. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    turquise	|     apricot	|      grey	|     lilac	|     black	|
| Nationality	|   nigerian	|    french	|    brazilian	|    mexican	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     rabbit	|    frog	|     chinchilla	|     goat	|      rat	|
| Beverage	|    fanta	|     7up	|     almond-milk	|    juice	|      soy-almond-milk	|
| Cigar		|   tiparillo	|    havana	|  montecristo	|    davidoff	|   apricotmaster	|
